<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "1,307 Cases of Illegal Crossings of </F>
Border"] 
  [Text] The Police Department of Debar stated at a press 
conference that it has registered 1,307 cases of illegal 
crossings of the Macedonian-Albanian border (1,303 of them being 
Albanian citizens), in the period of January-April this year. 
1,247 of the cases were underage youngsters, who have been 
returned to Albania by police intervention, whereas criminal 
charges have been brought against 56 individuals. The police 
representatives also informed of 11 border incidents near Debar 
in the same period. 

</TEXT>

