<F P=100> BULGARIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Internal Security Units Formed at Ministries </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Internal Security Units Formed at Ministries </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0905160294 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1500 
GMT 9 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0905160294 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Bulgarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] According to a government decision, units in charge 
of security and guarding facts, information, and objects that 
represent state security have been formed at the Council of 
Ministers, certain ministries, enterprises in the 
military-industrial complex, industrial plants, and 
representations across the border. The Ministry of Internal 
Affairs is responsible for the payroll and wages of these units' 
personnel. The employees will be officers of the National 
Security Service and the regional services. 

</TEXT>

