<H3> <TI>   KDNP Working To Mobilize Voters </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    KDNP Working To Mobilize Voters </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1105073994 Budapest MTI in English 1831 GMT 10 May 94 -- 
FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU1105073994 </F>
