were also questioned by the media because the ex-premier's 
co-workers and their relatives were to participate in the 
projects. 
  However, "the harmed entrepreneurs" at today's meeting 
maintained that the privatization projects were legally correct 
and were canceled for political reasons on minor pretexts. 

