<F P=102>   LD1005163594 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1600 
GMT 10 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1005163594 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network </F>
<F P=105>  Polish </F>


