<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] High-ranking sources within the Srpska army 
confirmed today the AFP report on the Muslim army's deployment 
of heavy weapons and troops on the southern foothills of Mount 
Igman [south of Sarajevo]. According to the same source, the 
weapons and troops were transferred via Sarajevo airport from 
the Muslim-held part of the city. [passage omitted] According 
to the same source, the Muslims have transferred 5,000 soldiers 
from Sarajevo to Mount Igman and Bjelasnica and, together with 
the forces deployed in the area previously and forces brought in 
from Konjic and Pazaric, they now have around 10,000 troops in 
the area, deployed in seven brigades. [passage omitted] 

