<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Belgrade, 11 May (TANJUG) -- On the basis of the 
decision by Sadako Ogata, UN high commissioner for refugees 
[UNHCR], employees of this organization will not be returning to 
the Srpska republic [RS], Koning Abuzaid, head of the UNHCR 
mission for former Bosnia-Herzegovina, said after today's visit 
to Brcko, the SRNA agency reports. 
  During a meeting today with Nikola Koljevic, RS vice 
