said this move was made because of a security threat to UNHCR 
personnel following the UN decision that Serb targets can be 
bombed without previous announcement. Humanitarian aid to the 
people in the Srpska republic will from now on be delivered via 
Belgrade, which is seen as technically more complicated. 

